metadata.name: Complicit #1 - Dennis in the Tree 1
metadata.description:
Complicit, photographs of older men, is about the existential reality all humans face. The work has been the recipient of fellowships and grants from the New York Foundation for the Arts, New York University, and Columbia University, and has been featured in magazines across the world, such as The New Yorker, Vice Magazine, Dazed Magazine, and Artnet.

Complicit collection was originally listed on an Opensea ERC-1155 smart contract on November 16, 2021. As of April 27, 2022, the project has a trading volume of 13.4ETH. 

The collection was updated to the current Complicit ERC-721 smart contract on April 28, 2022. Any additional trading volume must also take into account the initial trading volume of 13.4 ETH. 

Dennis in the Tree was originally purchased by stevecantor with wallet 0xa31A547758f695822fE582C76a6C404D5adC988F for 0.4 ETH on April 21, 2022
